eing%20resumed%2C%20but%20not%20through%20a%20formal%20declaration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Trudeau%20made%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%2C%20both%20countries%20had%20expelled%20one%20diplomat%20each.%20India%20had%20dismissed%20the%20accusations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%20and%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20New%20Delhi%20sought%20%E2%80%9Cparity%E2%80%9D%20and%20furnished%20a%20list%20of%20names%20to%20the%20Canadian%20side%20whose%20diplomatic%20immunity%20would%20be%20revoked%20if%20they%20did%20not%20leave%20by%20October%2010%2C%20which%20was%20later%20extended%20by%2010%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECanada%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20withdrawn%2041%20diplomats%20from%20India%20and%20stopped%20in-person%20facilities%20at%20three%20consulates%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700651753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-resumes-e-visa-services-canadians%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20had%20suspended%20all%20visa%20services%20after%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20India%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20separatist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-resumes-e-visa-services-canadians%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20was%20preparing%20its%20San%20Francisco%20offices%20with%20MacBooks%20and%20HR%20on%20standby%20to%20welcome%20defecting%20OpenAI%20employees%2C%20then%20Sam%20Altman%20rejoined%20as