shington%2C%20DC%2C%20invests%20about%20as%20much%20in%20long-term%20investments%20as%20he%20does%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-cost-of-living-alcohol-coffee-going-out-more-expensive-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efun%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20dinners%2C%20friends'%20weddings%2C%20and%20a%20trip%20to%20the%202026%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20how%20much%20money%20you%20make%2C%20it's%20more%20what%20you%20do%20with%20it%2C%20but%20when%20you%20make%20six%20figures%2C%20what%20you%20can%20do%20with%20it%20gives%20you%20a%20lot%20more%20freedom%20to%20live%20your%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Boresta%2C%20who%20works%20at%20a%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20master's%20of%20public%20administration%20graduate%20said%20he's%20still%20devoting%20around%20two-thirds%20of%20his%20income%20to%20necessities%20including%20rent%2C%20daily%20expenses%2C%20and%20debts.%20A%20fifth%20of%20his%20income%20goes%20to%20his%20401(k)%2C%20investments%20in%20mutual%20funds%2C%20and%20savings%20for%20rental%20properties%20a%20few%20years%20from%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20short-term%20worries%2C%20he%20hopes%20by%2035%2C%20he'll%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20have%20enough%20capital%20to%20start%20a%20family%20and%20have%20a%20rental%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20terribly%20motivated%20by%20money.%20It%20gives%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20freedom%20to%20have%20money%2C%20but%20in%20terms%20I%20need%20to%20be%20a%20millionaire%2C%20I%20need%20to%20have%20a%20company%2C%20that's%20not%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Boresta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20HENRYs%20are%20holding%20off%20on%20buying%20a%20home%20or%20starting%20a%20family%20until%20they're%20wealthier%2C%20others%20aren't%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20those%20life%20goals.%20Eric%2C%20who's%20in%20his%20early%2030s%20and%20lives%20in%20Ohio%2C%20bought%20a%20home%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20has%20young%20kids.%20Eric%2C%20who%20works%20in%20plastics%20manufacturing%20in%20Ohio%20and%20asked%20to%20just%20use%20his%20first%20name%20for%20privacy%20reasons%2C%20said%20he%20devotes%20money%20to%20travel%20and%20family%20outings%2C%20spends%20approximately%20%241%2C000%20on%20food%20each%20month%20for%20his%20family%2C%20and%20saves%20around%2030%25%20of%20his%20and%20his%20wife's%20combined%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20have%20a%20combined%20%24160%2C000%20salary%2C%20noticed%20that%20rising%20costs%20have%20led%20them%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20saving%20for%20his%20children's%20college%2C%20as%20well%20as%20reduce%20his%20brokerage%20investments%20and%20401(k)%20contribution.%20Though%2C%20he%20said%20he'll%20continue%20to%20devote%20money%20to%20what%20matters%20most%20to%20him%20amid%20high%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20older%20and%20closer%20to%20retirement%20with%20%241-2%20million%20in%20retirement%20savings%2C%20they're%20feeling%20the%20pinch%20as%20well%2C%20so%20it%20kind%20of%20made%20me%20feel%20better%20that%20I'm%20not%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Eric%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20HENRY%20who%20is%20worried%20about%20saving%20for%20the%20future%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenrys-saving-for-retirement-inflation-student-loans-credit-card-debt-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700651222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cd6dd22cf74a5739ac112%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenrys-saving-for-retirement-inflation-student-loan