5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655bb6049c7d23cb3b9d97e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Luban%20and%20Selena%20Medlen%20in%20Ronda%2C%20Spain.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Luban%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJason%20Luban%2C%2053%2C%20and%20Selena%20Medlen%2C%2045%2C%20left%20Oakland%2C%20California%2C%20for%20Ronda%2C%20Spain%2C%20in%202016.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20were%20tired%20of%20the%20Bay%20Area's%20cost%2C%20and%20found%20a%20cheaper%20and%20more%20meaningful%20life%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20they%20work%20less%20and%20earn%20enough%20income%20to%20cover%20their%20expenses%20and%20save%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jason%20Luban%2C%20a%20medical%20practice%20consultant%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Selena%20Medlen%2C%20an%20attorney%2C%20who%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20relocate%20from%20their%20longtime%20home%20of%20Oakland%2C%20California%2C%20to%20Ronda%2C%20Spain%2C%20in%202023.%20The%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20met%20in%20California%20and%20we%20both%20had%20already%20been%20there%20for%20a%20while.%20I%20started%20a%20clinic%20and%20built%20it%20up%2C%20so%20that%20kept%20me%20there.%20We%20never%20knew%20anything%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20just%20a%20good%20place%20to%20be%20economically%20and%20build%20your%20career%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunity%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Before%20we%20moved%2C%20we%20had%20experienced%20a%20series%20of%20losses.%20We%20had%20tried%20for%20years%20to%20have%20kids%2C%20and%20had%20just%20had%20a%20very%20expensive%20failed%20round%20of%20IVF.%20In%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20acupuncturist%2C%20I%20was%20so%20stressed%20out%20that%20I%20became%20an%20insomniac%20and%20basically%20forgot%20how%20to%20sleep.%20Our%20dog%20had%20just%20died%2C%20my%20mentor%20as%20well%2C%20and%20though%20we%20were%20making%20a%20good%20living%2C%20the%20expense%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20was%20wearing%20us%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20really%20thought%20we%20needed%20a%20break%20from%20our%20current%20lives%20and%20just%20sort%20of%20a%20reset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20we%20had%20a%20long-planned%20two%20week%20trip%20to%20southern%20Spain%20on%20the%20books.%20We%20were%20enchanted%20by%20the%20village%20of%20Ronda%2C%20midway%20between%20Seville%20and%20Granada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ronda's%20landscape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655b9f594ca513d8242c5156%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERonda's%20landscape.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Luban%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20both%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Ronda%20because%20of%20how%20beautiful%20it%20was.%20It%20was%20full%20of%20wildflowers%20and%20greenery.%20We%20also%20saw%20that%20the%20rents%20were%20so%20much%20lower%20than%20in%20Oakland.%20Around%20that%20time%2C%20the%20dollar%20was%20pretty%20strong%20against%20the%20euro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20were%20so%20desperate%20for%20change%20that%20on%20the%20way%20home%2C%20my%20wife%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20would%20sell%20your%20practice%2C%20I%20would%20move%20to%20Ronda.%26quot%3B%20I%20sold%20it%20in%20six%20weeks.%20In%202016%2C%20three%20months%20after%20first%20visiting%20our%20village%2C%20we%20were%20moving%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20are%20saving%20money%20and%20making%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERonda%20is%20picturesque.%20It%20is%20surrounded%20by%20mountain%20ranges%20and%20undulating%20hills.%20Its%20farmland%20is%20very%20well%20preserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20visited%20by%20tourists%20from%20around%20the%20world%20all%20year%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20feel%20like%20you're%20isolated%20from%20the%20world%2C%20but%20in%20a%20way%20it's%20kind%20of%20apart%20from%20the%20buzz%20of%20a%20modern%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20morning%20we%20can%20go%20for%20a%20walk%20and%20bike%20ride.%20We%20can%20work%20from%20anywhere%20and%20also%20get%20on%20a%20plane%20to%20travel%20anywhere%20in%20Europe%20within%20an%20hour%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luban%20cycling%20in%20Ronda%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655b9f209c7d23cb3b9d7e88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuban%20cycling%20in%20Ronda%2C%20Spain.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Luban%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We've%20downsized%20significantly%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20Probably%20900%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20paying%20%E2%82%AC600%20per%20month%20for%20a%20three-bedroom%2C%20two-bath%20apartment%20with%20great%20views.%20It's%201%2F6%20of%20what%20we%20paid%20in%20rent%20for%20our%20home%20in%20Oakland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20last%20year%20we%20were%20in%20Oakland%2C%20our%20monthly%20expenses%2C%20including%20rent%2C%20were%20%243%2C500%20plus%20utilities.%20It%20would%20be%20over%20%245%2C000%20for%20the%20house%20now%20to%20rent%20it%20out.%20By%20living%20in%20Ronda%2C%20our%20monthly%20total%20is%20thousands%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20have%20private%20healthcare%20that%20is%20about%201%2F10%20the%20cost%20that%20we%20were%20paying%20for%20a%20good%20health%20plan%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20with%20zero%20deductibles%2C%20including%20dental%20care.%20The%20cost%20of%20food%20and%20going%20out%20is%20about%2025%25%20of%20what%20it%20would%20be%20had%20we%20stayed%20in%20California.%20We%20can%20leave%20our%20place%20unlocked%20and%20my%20wife%20can%20walk%20the%20dog%20at%20midnight%20without%20worrying%20about%20a%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22841%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jason%20Luban%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20a%20local%20friend.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655ba1374ca513d8242c52f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20a%20cycling%20accident%2C%20Luban's%20friend%20stopped%20by%20to%20check%20on%20him.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Luban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20really%20the%20people%20that%20keep%20us%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20levels%20of%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20place%3A%20One%20is%20you%20meet%20all%20the%20expats%2C%20which%20is%20the%20easy%20first%20thing%20you%20do%2C%20and%20the%20second%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20important%20and%20not%20everybody%20does%20it%20%E2%80%94%20is%20to%20really%20try%20to%20get%20involved%20with%20the%20local%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20in%20Ronda%20are%20some%20of%20the%20friendliest%20people%20anywhere.%20You%20can%20walk%20outside%20with%20a%20dog%20and%20you'll%20make%20a%20new%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20quality%20of%20life%20has%20improved%20greatly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We're%20not%20100%25%20sure%20that%20we%20want%20to%20live%20here%20forever.%20We%20re-evaluate%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Although%20there%20are%20tons%20of%20stories%20about%20how%20great%20and%20how%20easy%20and%20cheap%20it%20is%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20thing%20is%2C%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20bureaucracy%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20governmental%20situation%20that%20you%20are%20not%20familiar%20with%20%E2%80%94%20and%20will%20never%20be%20familiar%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20don't%20have%20disclosures%20and%20there's%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20buyer's%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20one%20looking%20out%20for%20you%20unless%20you%20hire%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luban%20and%20Medlen%20with%20friends.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655b9fd04ca513d8242c51b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22894%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuban%20and%20Medlen%20with%20friends.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Luban%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EIt%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%20to%20be%20this%20far%20away%20from%20our%20families%2C%20but%20the%20ability%20to%20work%20only%2020%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20more%20than%20cover%20all%20of%20our%20expenses%2C%20as%20well%20as%20put%20money%20into%20retirement%2C%20keeps%20us%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedlen%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20bigger%20benefits%20for%20us%20is%20that%20we%20have%20more%20because%20of%20the%20lower%20cost%20of%20living.%20We%20don't%20feel%20the%20pressure%20to%20keep%20making%20more%20and%20more%20every%20year%20because%20prices%20are%20going%20up.%20We%20can%20work%20less%20and%20earn%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuban%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20incredible%20to%20realize%20now%20how%20stressed%20out%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20keep%20our%20lives%20going%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20We%20still%20make%20money%20in%20US%20dollars%2C%20and%20we%20pay%20US%20taxes.%20But%20it's%20incredible%20to%20realize%20what%20a%20toll%20the%20stress%20of%20life%20there%20was%20taking%20on%20us.%20There's%20no%20way%20to%20really%