0affordability%20will%20worsen%2C%20while%20others%20say%20prices%20are%20on%20their%20way%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20affordability%20crisis%20in%20the%20US%20is%20bad%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20America's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eneighbors%20to%20the%20north%20may%20have%20it%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20home%20value%20in%20Canada%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-65688460%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20doubled%20since%202011%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20country%20is%20also%20almost%20certainly%20heading%20towards%20a%20recession%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0if%20it's%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-31%2Fcanada-economy-on-track-to-enter-technical-recession%3FleadSource%3Dreddit_wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20in%20one%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20housing%20market%20is%20partly%20to%20blame%2C%20economists%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drivers%3F%20Demand%20has%20raced%20ahead%20of%20supply.%20The%20country%20simply%20isn't%20building%20enough%20housing.%20City%20governments%2C%20which%20largely%20control%20housing%20policy%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bbiased%20towards%20homeowners%20and%20not%20towards%20renters%2C%26quot%3B%20Concordia%20University%20economist%20Mosche%20Lander%20argued%2C%20supporting%20policies%20that%20limit%20homebuilding%20and%20keep%20home%20values%20elevated.%20Investors%20pouring%20money%20into%20real%20estate%20speculation%20haven't%20helped.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F03%2F22%2Famericas%2Fcanada-record-population-growth-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%20population%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20immigration%20has%20only%20added%20to%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20sound%20familiar.%20The%20combination%20of%20a%20housing%20shortage%2C%20rising%20interest%20rates%2C%20and%20investor%20speculation%20have%20al