shing%20their%20dollars%20at%20the%20singer.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-money-jobs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eestimates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20her%20Eras%20Tour%20has%20given%20the%20US%20a%20%245.7%20billion%20boost%2C%20with%20Swifties%20spending%20around%20%2493%20million%20per%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demographics%20of%20Swift%20fans%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20spending%20power%20that%20has%20been%20touted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftaylor-swifts-economic-impact-catches-attention-federal-reserve-hotel-revenue-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20Philadelphia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20who%20are%20the%20typical%20Swift%20fans%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESwifties%20lean%20female%20and%20white%2C%20make%20under%20%2450%2C000%2C%20and%20are%20suburban%20millennials%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20under%20three-quarters%20of%20self-identifying%20avid%20Swift%20fans%20are%20white%2C%20while%2013%25%20are%20Black%20and%209%25%20are%20Asian%2C%20according%20to%20Morning%20Consult's%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20while%20Swift%20fans%20skew%20female%2C%2048%25%20of%20those%20Swift%20fans%20are%20male.%20Similarly%2C%20avid%20Swift%20fans%20are%20concentrated%20in%20the%20suburbs%2C%20with%2055%25%20living%20in%20suburban%20communities%2C%20and%20a%20fairly%20even%20split%20among%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%3B%2026%25%20are%20city%20dwellers%2C%20while%2021%25%20are%20rural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20line%20with%20Swift's%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-voting-joe-biden-president-endorsement-v-magazine-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolitical%20proclamations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2055%25%20of%20avid%20Swift%20fans%20are%20Democrats.%20The%20remainder%20of%20the%20fans%20are%20equally%20split%20among%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eidentifying%20as%20Republicans%20and%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20even%20as%20many%20Swift%20fans%20are%20spending%20thousands%20on%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20most%20are%20not%20high-earners.%20Just%20about%20half%20of%20Swift%20fans%20make%20under%20%2450%2C000%2C%20while%2025%25%20make%20between%20%2450%2C000%20and%20%24100%2C000%2C%20and%20the%20other%20quarter%20make%20%24100%2C000%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20fairly%20stark%20figure%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20%241%2C300%20that%20Swifties%20spend%20on%20average%20to%20attend%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F06%2F07%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-chicago-hotel-booking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eper%20research%20company%20QuestionPro%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20while%20some%20Swifties%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-taylor-swift-fans-spend-concerts-eras-tour-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20spoke%20to%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20they%20were%20spending%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20to%20attend%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20some%20were%20able%20to%20keep%20their%20costs%20in%20the%20hundreds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwifties%20also%20lean%20millennial%2C%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20generation%20making%20up%2045%25%20of%20self-proclaimed%20avid%20fans.%20Additionally%2C%2023%25%20of%20those%20fans%20are%20baby%20boomers%2C%20and%2021%25%20are%20Gen%20X.%20Meanwhile%2C%20just%2011%25%20of%20that%20fan%20group%20are%20Gen%20Z.%20However%2C%20Briggs%20noted%20that%20the%20survey%20only%20took%20the%20pulse%20of%20Americans%2018%20or%20older%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20that%20the%20younger%20Gen%20Z%20contingent%20is%20not%20necessarily%20reflected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMillennials%20are%20in%20their%20peak%20spending%20years%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%26quot