%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-friday-cyber-monday-holiday-shopping-discounts-sales-prices-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Feel%20Personal%20Pride%26quot%3B%3A%20Child%20Abuse%20Victim%20Who%20Forced%20Omegle%20To%20Shut%20Down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnline%20chat%20platform%20Omegle%20officially%20shut%20down%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20a%2014-year%20run.%20Introduced%20in%202009%2C%20this%20free%20service%20was%20known%20for%20randomly%20matching%20users%20for%20anonymous%20one-on-one%20conversations.%20Founder%20Leif%20K-Brooks%20cited%20the%20substantial%20costs%20of%20managing%20Omegle%20and%20addressing%20potential%20misuse%20as%20the%20primary%20reasons%20behind%20the%20site's%20shutdown.%20Now%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20forced%20the%20site%20to%20shut%20has%20spoken%20about%20the%20same.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20feels%20a%20sense%20of%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20pride%26quot%3B%20as%20%26quot%3Bno%20more%20children%20will%20be%20added%20to%20Omegle's%20body%20count%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67485561%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlice%20or%20%26quot%3BA.M.%26quot%3B%20as%20she's%20referred%20to%20in%20court%20filings%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20on%20Omegle%20and%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20she%20demanded%20the%20website's%20removal%20as%20part%20of%20an%20out-of-court%20settlement.%20She%20claims%20the%20%26quot%3Boutpouring%20of%20gratitude%26quot%3B%20has%20%26quot%3Bvalidated%26quot%3B%20her%20since%20people%20have%20shared%20disturbing%20stories%20regarding%20the%20site.%20She%20has%20spent%20years%20demanding%20compensation%20after%20being%20linked%20at%20random%20with%20a%20paedophile%20who%20turned%20her%20into%20his%20digital%20sex%20slave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20able%20to%20manipulate%20me%20immediately%2C%20and%20very%20quickly%20I%20was%20being%20forced%20to%20do%20things%20that%20a%20child%20should%20not%20have%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BBC%20in%20an%20old%20documentary%20on%20Omegle.%20Alice%20filed%20her%20groundbreaking%20lawsuit%20in%202021%2C%20about%20the%20time%20her%20abuser%2C%20Ryan%20Fordyce%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20eight%20years%20in%20jail%20in%20Canada.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20three%20years%20of%20abuse%2C%20Fordyce%20gathered%20220%20pictures%20and%20videos%20of%20Alice%2C%20who%20was%2011%20at%20the%20time%2C%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20acts%20under%20his%20coercion.%20He%20had%20done%20the%20same%20to%20five%20other%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20her%20court%20battle%2C%20Alice%20stated%20that%20she%20intended%20to%20proceed%20with%20a%20jury%20trial%20to%20receive%20around%20%2422%20million%20in%20damages.%20However%2C%20she%20now%20claims%20that%20it%20was%20better%20for%20her%20and%20others%20to%20settle%20out%20of%20court%20earlier%20this%20month%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20the%20site%20shut%20down%20was%20something%20I%20couldn't%20have%20achieved%20in%20court%2C%20so%20I%20got%20to%20tailor%20the%20outcome.%20Accomplishing%20everything%20we%20were%20able%20to%20in%20court%20and%20then%20obtaining%20this%20result%20now%20-%20probably%20years%20earlier%20than%20we%20could%20have%20reached%20a%20jury%20verdict%20-%20is%20something%20I'll%20never%20stop%20being%20proud%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlice%20expressed%20gratitude%20that%20%26quot%3BOmegle%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20on%20my%20mind%20from%20sunrise%20to%20sunset%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20she%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20lead%20a%20normal%20life%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Mr%20Brooks%20in%20his%20statement%20about%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20website%20mentioned%20the%20woman%20and%20thanked%20her%20%26quot%3Bfor%20opening%