0out%20of%20his%20house%20in%20northwest%20Bengaluru's%20Palace%20Guttahalli%20area%20to%20get%20some%20medicines%20from%20a%20shop%20nearby.%20When%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20parking%20area%20after%20buying%20the%20medicines%2C%20he%20saw%20a%20man%20on%20a%20bike%20hitting%20his%20two-wheeler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnappa%20went%20up%20to%20the%20man%2C%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20ride%20properly.%20This%20angered%20Khan%20and%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20stone%2C%20hit%20Krishnappa%20and%20fled.%20Passersby%20noticed%20the%20elderly%20man%20lying%20on%20the%20road%2C%20assumed%20he%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20passing%20vehicle%20and%20took%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20died%20during%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSarfaraz%20Khan%20is%20a%20known%20motorcycle%20thief.%20He%20had%20stolen%20a%20parked%20motorcycle%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20leave%20with%20it%20when%20he%20hit%20Krishnappa's%20two-wheeler.%20An%20argument%20between%20them%20led%20to%20Krishnappa%20being%20assaulted%20with%20a%20stone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20police%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20known%20to%20the%20police%20at%20the%20time%2C%20who%20registered%20a%20hit-and-run%20case%20and%20informed%20Krishnappa's%20son%2C%20Satish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatish%20found%20the%20accident%20theory%20hard%20to%20believe%20and%2C%20after%20taking%20some%20time%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20shock%2C%20decided%20to%20check%20the%20footage%20from%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20in%20the%20medical%20shop%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20footage%20revealed%20the%20assault%20and%20Satish%20informed%20the%20police%2C%20who%20then%20registered%20a%20murder%20case%20and%20arrested%20Khan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Shekhar%20T%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BKrishnappa%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20VG%20Colony.%20He%20died%20when%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20buy%20some%20medicines%20and%20a%20hit-and-run%