usands%20of%20students%20preparing%20for%20NEET-JEE%20exams%2C%20has%20unfortunately%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20suicides%20this%20year.%20On%20this%20matter%2C%20Dhariwal%20chose%20not%20to%20delve%20into%20specifics%20and%20simply%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cold%20matter%E2%80%9D%20that%20he%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Dhariwal%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20projects%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Rs%2014%2C000%20crore%20Chambal%20riverfront%20development%20%E2%80%93%20ran%20into%20controversy%20this%20year.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20riverfront%20construction%20has%20adversely%20affected%20wildlife.%20Former%20MLA%20Prahlad%20Gunjal%20from%20Kota%20(North)%20contended%20that%20the%20area%2C%20where%20the%20riverfront%20is%20located%2C%20is%20a%20crocodile%20sanctuary%20with%20a%20designated%20eco-sensitive%20zone%20extending%20up%20to%2010%20kilometres.%20The%20matter%20is%20set%20to%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%2C%20and%20Dhariwal%20asserted%20his%20openness%20to%20scrutiny%2C%20emphasising%20that%20all%20necessary%20steps%20were%20taken%20before%20initiating%20the%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20finalising%20his%20ticket%20and%20rumours%20of%20corruption%2C%20Dhariwal%20clarified%20that%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20many%20people%20complained%20against%20him%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20This%20prompted%20an%20investigation%20by%20a%20team%20set%20up%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Dhariwal%20was%20subsequently%20cleared%20of%20any%20corruption%20allegations%20and%20granted%20the%20party%20ticket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDhariwal%E2%80%99s%20name%20has%20become%20a%20catchphrase%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20discourse%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20elections%20because%20of%20a%20controversial%20statement%20he%20made%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20where%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emardon%3C%2Fem%3E%20ka%20pradesh%20hai%20(It%E2%80%99s%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20land).%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20defence%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20did%20say%20that%2C%20but%20why%20is%20the%20opposition%20only%20questioning%20that%20part%3F%20Why%20are%20they%20not%20showing%20the%20complete%20video%20where%20I%20also%20criticised%20this%20serious%20issue%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Rajasthan%20gears%20up%20for%20elections%20on%20November%2025%2C%20these%20developments%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20dynamic%20political%20landscape%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700649903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F10122409%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Frajasthan-polls-minister-shanti-dhariwal-interview%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhariwal's%20name%20has%20become%20a%20catchphrase%20in%20the%20state's%20political%20discourse%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20assembly%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Frajasthan-polls-minister-shanti-dhariwal-interview%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Be%20warned%3A%20Flights%20are%20getting%20bumpier%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Illustration%20of%20a%20plane%20tray%20table%20with%20spilled%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d0c754ca513d8242d31d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAir%20turbulence%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%20And%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20flights%20a%20whole%20lot%20bumpier.%20%3Cp%3EBen%20Hickey%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20suddenly%20dropped%20several%20feet%2C%20flew%20up%2C%20then%20lurched%20back%20down.%20I%20held%20my%20breath%2C%20bracing%20for%20the%20inevitable%20bobbing%20to%20repeat.%20The%20flight%20attendant%20offered%20me%20a%20barf%20bag%20and%20a%20conciliatory%20smile.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-climate-change-is-making-plane-turbulence-worse-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturbulence%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn't%20her%20fault%20%E2%80%94%20it%20wasn't%20even%20the%20pilot's.%20Yet%20for%2020%20minutes%20on%20my%20flight%20from%20Denver%20to%20my%20home%20in%20Indianapolis%2C%20the%20plane%20jerked%20up%20and%20down%2C%20sometimes%20so%20violently%20passengers%20let%20out%20a%20collective%20gasp%20that%20rattled%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20frightened%20of%20both%20flying%20and%20heights%20%E2%80%94%20to%20my%20core.%20I%20wondered%20if%20it%20was%20the%20last%20flight%20I'd%20ever%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20was%20not%20an%20outlier.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-turbulence-causes-dangerous-airplanes-flight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20turbulence%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20becoming%20more%20common%20and%20more%20intense.%20On%20this%20particular%20flight%2C%20we%20experienced%20mountain-wave%20turbulence%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bumpiness%20that%20sometimes%20happens%20when%20flying%20over%20mountainous%20regions.%20Other%20kinds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsevere-air-turbulence-has-increased-by-55-since-1979-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturbulence%3C%2Fa%3E%20include%20the%20bumps%20caused%20by%20thunderstorms%20and%20clear-air%20turbulence.%20Researchers%20say%20this%20last%20one%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20and%20it%20may%20have%20made%20my%20regular%20'ol%20mountain-wave%20turbulence%20more%20fraught.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClear-air%20turbulence%20happens%20without%20bad%20weather%2C%20mountains%2C%20or%20mechanical%20issues%20with%20a%20plane.%20It's%20caused%20by%20wind%20shear%20%E2%80%94%20sudden%20changes%20in%20wind%20speed%20often%20associated%20with%20the%20jet%20stream%2C%20a%20strong%20band%20of%20wind%20high%20up%20in%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20Isabel%20Smith%2C%20a%20meteorology%20Ph.D.%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Reading%20in%20England%2C%20told%20me.%20Smith%20and%20her%20advisor%2C%20Paul%20Williams%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20atmospheric%20science%2C%20have%20found%20that%20since%201979%20%E2%80%94%20when%20satellites%20first%20started%20observing%20the%20atmosphere%20%E2%80%94%20clear-air%20turbulence%20has%20jumped%2015%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20caused%20flights%20around%20the%20world%20to%20get%20bumpier.%20This%20past%20March%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Flufthansa-flight-hits-severe-turbulence-dog-owner-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELufthansa%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20to%20Frankfurt%2C%20Germany%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Flufthansa-flight-crew-delete-photos-severe-turbulence-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eso%20bumpy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%C2%A0seven%20passengers%20were%20injured.%20The%20plane%20had%20to%20be%20diverted%20to%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fflight-turbulence-increasing-from-climate-change-expert-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculprit%20behind%20the%20newly%20turbulent%20skies%20is%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Smith%20said.%20As%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions%20like%20carbon%20dioxide%20rise%2C%20so%20do%20global%20temperatures%2C%20making%20the%20jet%20stream%20carry%20more%20wind%20shear%20that%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3Bspeed%20bumps%20in%20the%20sky%26quot%3B%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20or%20turbulence.%20It's%20a%20problem%20that%20isn't%20going%20away.%20In%202017%2C%20Williams%20used%20climate%20model%20simulations%20to%20predict%20future%20turbulence.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1002%2F2017GL074618%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20clear-air%20turbulence%20in%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%20could%20triple%20in%20the%20next%20three%20to%20six%20decades.%20And%20as%20emissions%20increase%2C%20so%20will%20overall%20turbulence.%20It's%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20that's%20ushering%20in%20a%20new%20reality%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-travel-airline-customer-service-airports-delayed-canceled-flights-terrible-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20already%20been%20plagued%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Faviation-experts-why-its-a-nightmare-to-fly-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproblems%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20pandemic%20hit.%20So%20next%20time%20you%20travel%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20pack%20your%20Ambien%2C%20because%20it's%20going%20to%20get%20bumpy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpeed%20bumps%20in%20the%20sky%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20works%3A%20As%20emissions%20from%20greenhouse%20gases%20spread%20through%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20the%20upper%20levels%20of%20the%20sky%20develop%20unpredictable%20patterns%20of%20warm%20and%20cold%20air%20spots%2C%20which%20make%20the%20air%20bumpier%20for%20planes.%20The%20rising%20temperatures%20caused%20by%20greenhouse%20gases%20also%20drive%20more%20extreme%20weather%2C%20which%20disrupts%20the%20jet%20stream%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Duncan%2C%20the%20aviation-forecast%20operations%20leader%20at%20The%20Weather%20Company%2C%20told%20me%20the%20jet%20stream%20has%20changed%20from%20what%20we%20saw%2020%20to%2030%20years%20ago.%20%26quot%3BThe%20jet%20stream%20is%20now%20wobbling%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20likely%20heard%20articles%20speak%20of%20polar%20vortex%2C%20for%20example.%20As%20the%20jet%20stream%20buckles%20a%20bit%20because%20it's%20not%20as%20strong%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20past%2C%20now%20you%20have%20all%20this%20energy%20associated%20with%20the%20jet%20stream%20up%2030%2C000%20feet%20or%20so.%20It's%20allowing%20colder%20air%20to%20spill%20south%2C%20so%20we're%20seeing%20major%20weather%20events%20happening%20more%20and%20more%20than%20we%20did%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20increase%20in%20clear-air%20turbulence%20is%20supercharging%20other%20kinds%20of%20turbulence%2C%20such%20as%20the%20mountain-air%20turbulence%20that%20I%20experienced%20over%20Denver.%20%26quot%3BThis%20type%20of%20turbulence%20is%20generated%20from%20air%20flow%20being%20forced%20over%20a%20mountainous%20terrain%20and%20becoming%20very%20unstable%2C%20leading%20to%20waves%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20that%20can%20break%20and%20become%20chaotic%20and%20dangerous%20to%20encounter%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%2C%20the%20Ph.D.%20student%2C%20said.%20Given%20its%20position%20downwind%20of%20the%20Rocky%20Mountains%2C%20Denver%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.ametsoc.org%2Fview%2Fjournals%2Fapme%2F47%2F8%2F2008jamc1799.1.xml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehot%20spot%20for%20mountain-wave%20turbulence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20any%20flight%20path%20that%20goes%20over%20a%20mountainous%20area%20or%20along%20a%20coast%2C%20where%20temperatures%20can%20shift%20unexpectedly%2C%20is%20prone%20to%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20last%20flight%2C%20Denver%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20on%20my%20list%20of%20vacation%20spots.%20But%20no%20flight%20path%20or%20airport%20is%20really%20safe%20from%20increasing%20turbulence.%20%26quot%3BAll%20types%20of%20aviation%20turbulence%20are%20likely%20to%20increase%20in%20the%20future%2C%20in%20all%20seasons%20in%20most%20places%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20K.%20Williams%2C%20the%20head%20of%20weather%20AI%20sciences%20at%20The%20Weather%20Company%2C%20explained.%20%26quot%3BPerhaps%20even%20doubling%20in%20some%20places.%26quot%3B%20Weather%20conditions%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20spring%20are%20typically%20more%20stable%2C%20so%20flying%20conditions%20are%20generally%20calmer%2C%20Smith%20said%2C%20but%20those%20seasons%20could%20become%20increasingly%20erratic%20as%20the%20air%20pressure%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20turbulent%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20airlines%20could%20decrease%20the%20chances%20of%20hitting%20clear-air%20turbulence%20by%20avoiding%20the%20Earth's%20four%20main%20jet%20streams%20altogether.%20Commercial%20airlines%20tend%20to%20rely%20on%20these%20strong%20wind%20corridors%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20boost%20to%20reduce%20flight%20times%20and%20fuel%20use%20%E2%80%94%20kind%20of%20like%20walking%20on%20a%20moving%20sidewalk.%20But%20changes%20to%20the%20atmosphere%20mean%20these%20corridors%20are%20getting%20bumpier%2C%20so%20avoiding%20them%20could%20result%20in%20smoother%20flights.%20However%2C%20the%20experts%20I%20spoke%20with%20didn't%20think%20this%20was%20a%20real%20solution.%20Without%20the%20jet%20streams%2C%20flights%20would%20be%20longer%20and%20require%20more%20fuel%2C%20making%20them%20more%20expensive%20and%20worse%20for%20the%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20not%20really%20an%20appealing%20option%20for%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20pilots%20will%20likely%20have%20to%20take%20different%20flight%20paths%20to%20avoid%20turbulence.%20Duncan%20explained%20that%20meteorologists%2C%20dispatchers%2C%20and%20pilots%20can%20adjust%20a%20flight%20path%20based%20on%20timely%20weather%20data.%20Right%20now%2C%20this%20information%20is%20often%20too%20delayed%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20but%20as%20the%20weather-modeling%20tech%20improves%2C%20that%20could%20change.%20And%20that's%20what%20John%20K.%20Williams%20is%20betting%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20years%2C%20our%20ability%20to%20predict%20the%20location%2C%20timing%20and%20severity%20of%20turbulence%20have%20also%20improved%2C%20and%20those%20predictions%20can%20be%20used%20by%20airlines%20and%20pilots%20to%20select%20less%20bumpy%20routes%2C%20or%20at%20least%20prepare%20passengers%20and%20flight%20crews%20for%20flight%20segments%20into%20turbulent%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20these%20improvements%20is%20AI.%20%26quot%3BMachine-learning%20algorithms%20are%20used%20to%20find%20relationships%20between%20historical%20weather%20and%20observations%20of%20turbulence%2C%20improving%20themselves%20as%20more%20data%20are%20collected%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThose%20algorithms%20can%20then%20be%20run%20using%20the%20latest%20weather%20forecast%20model%20data%20to%20pinpoint%20areas%20of%20potentially%20hazardous%20turbulence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20we%20can%20get%20better%20at%20avoiding%20air%20turbulence%2C%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20avoid%20it%20altogether.%20That's%20why%20some%20companies%20are%20going%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%20to%20design%20airplanes%20that%20can%20better%20adjust%20to%20turbulent%20air.%20The%20Swiss%20company%20Neural%20Concept%2C%20which%20uses%20AI-generated%20simulations%20to%20help%20industrial%20companies%20improve%20their%20engineering%2C%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20the%20airplane%20manufacturer%20Airbus%20to%20improve%20its%20aircraft%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigning%20an%20airplane%20that's%20more%20steady%20in%20turbulent%20air%20is%20tricky%20because%20there%20are%20so%20many%20variables%20to%20account%20for%2C%20Pierre%20Baqu%C3%A9%2C%20Neural%20Concept's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20AI%20becomes%20critical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBy%20applying%20deep%20learning%20models%20to%20the%20database%20of%20simulations%2C%20aircraft%20manufacturers%20can%20gain%20real-time%20insights%20into%20the%20correlation%20between%20tens%20of%20statistically%20averaged%20variables%20that%20might%20impact%20turbulence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages%2C%20so%20it%20could%20be%20years%20before%20we%20see%20the%20results%20of%20this%20work%20in%20commercial%20aircraft.%20And%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20unpredictable%20air%20remains%20a%20problem.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fturbulence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E163%20serious%20injuries%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20turbulence%20since%202009.%20To%20keep%20flight%20attendants%20and%20passengers%20safe%2C%20some%20flights%20might%20have%20to%20cancel%20meal%20service%2C%20restrict%20passengers'%20ability%20to%20stand%20up%20or%20use%20the%20restroom%2C%20and%20limit%20the%20availability%20of%20flight%20attendants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fly%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%20and%20I%20see%20people%20walk%20around%20all%20the%20time%20even%20when%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20is%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Duncan%20said.%20%26quot%3BTurbulence%20is%20tricky%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20turbulence%20can%20come%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20And%20you%20never%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20shear%20that%20aircraft%20will%20go%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlyson%20Smith%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20emotional%20health%20and%20well-being%20programs%20at%20Delta%2C%20said%20passengers%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20avoiding%20a%20turbulent%20flight%20if%20they%20fly%20very%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20late%20at%20night.%20%26quot%3BTurbulence%20is%20generally%20the%20lowest%20during%20these%20time%20periods%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20passengers%20can%20do%20is%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20flight%20crew%20and%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20seatbelt%20sign.%20For%20me%20at%20least%2C%20I'll%20be%20staying%20buckled%20up%20while%20I'm%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fmichelle-mastro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMichelle%20Mastro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20writer%20who%C2%A0covers%20lifestyle%2C%20travel%2C%20architecture%2C%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbulence-getting-worse-cause-climate-change-bumpy-flight-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700649902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d0c8d22cf74a5739b19f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbulence-getting-worse-cause-climate-change-bumpy-flight-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20travel%20is%20getting%20more%20turbulent%20thanks%20to%20climate%20change.%20And%20the%20problem%20isn't%20going%20away.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michelle%20Mastro)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbulence-getting-worse-cause-climate-change-bumpy-flight-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahn%20on%20shooting%20with%20a%20pregnant%20Lee%20Da%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700649872000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105415863%2Cimgsize-42870.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fahn-eun-jin-on-shooting-with-a-pregnant-lee-da-in-for-my-dearest-i-was-even-more-worried-about-her-than-herself%2Farticleshow%2F105415876.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105415876.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActress%20Ahn%20Eun-jin%20reflected%20on%20her%20transformative%20journey%20during%20the%20sh