h%20a%20degree%20in%20physics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20founded%20FTX%2C%20which%20skyrocketed%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20crypto%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20built%20up%20his%20image%20as%20the%20unofficial%20ambassador%20for%20the%20cryptocurrency%20industry%2C%20with%20high-profile%20appearances%20in%20the%20media%20and%20even%20the%20US%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20in%202022%2C%20he%20had%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%2424%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20had%20been%20walking%20a%20dangerous%20path%20--%20his%20team%20used%20customers'%20money%20for%20everything%20from%20buying%20posh%20real%20estate%20to%20covering%20risky%20moves%20by%20affiliate%20Alameda%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20came%20crashing%20down%20when%20these%20moves%20were%20revealed%20in%20the%20media%20in%20November%202022.%20Within%20hours%2C%20rival%20CZ%20Zhao%20said%20Binance%20would%20sell%20all%20the%20FTX%20tokens%20it%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sparked%20a%20stunning%20collapse%20of%20FTX%20and%20Bankman-Fried's%20empire%2C%20his%20fame%20turning%20to%20notoriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArrested%20in%20the%20Bahamas%20in%20January%2C%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%20this%20month%20of%20what%20US%20prosecutors%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20biggest%20financial%20frauds%20in%20American%20history%26quot%3B.%20He%20faces%20up%20to%20110%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20trial%2C%20the%2031-year-old%20admitted%20to%20making%20%26quot%3Bmistakes%26quot%3B%20but%20denied%20trying%20to%20defraud%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20Kwon%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20entrepreneur%20Do%20Kwon%20co-founded%20Terraform%20Labs%20in%202018%2C%20developing%20the%20cryptocurrencies%20TerraUSD%20and%20Luna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Stanford%20grad%20successfully%20marketed%20them%20as%20the%20next%20big%20thing%20in%20crypto%2C%20attracting%20billions%20in%20investments%20and%20global%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%20reports%20in%20South%20Korea%20described%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenius%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20the%20value%20of%20these%20currencies%20--%20marketed%20as%20%26quot%3Bstablecoins%26quot%3B%20--%20plummeted%2C%20wiping%20out%20around%20%2440%20billion%20in%20investments%20and%20sending%20a%20shock%20wave%20through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20to%20more%20than%20%24500%20billion%20in%20further%20losses%20on%20global%20crypto%20markets%2C%20industry%20data%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20said%20Do%20Kwon%20--%20whose%20full%20name%20is%20Kwon%20Do-kyung%20--%20had%20marketed%20a%20glorified%20Ponzi%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrash%20and%20outspoken%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Do%20Kwon%20left%20South%20Korea%20before%20the%20collapse%20and%20spent%20months%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20in%20Montenegro%20this%20year%20after%20being%20caught%20trying%20to%20catch%20a%20flight%20using%20fake%20Costa%20Rican%20travel%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faces%20multiple%20criminal%20charges%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700644980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fpmblfp2g_sam-bankmanfried-reuters_625x300_21_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fterraform-labs-binance-ftx-changpeng-cz-zhao-sam-bankman-fried-do-kwon-from-kings-of-crypto-to-convicts-list-of-3-fallen-crypto-executives-4596073%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Binance%20boss%20Changpeng%20Zhao%20has%20become