roudly%20championing%20it%20as%20evidence%20of%20the%20growth%20and%20development%20promised%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funderstanding-gdp-growth-through-discrepancies-and-why-the-major-push-is-not-visible%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20GDP%20Growth%20Through%20Discrepancies%20and%20Why%20the%20Major%20Push%20Is%20Not%20Visible%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20why%20boast%20about%20a%20growing%20GDP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20a%20growing%20GDP%20is%20a%20way%20to%20showcase%20economic%20success%20during%20the%20current%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20It%20suggests%20that%20policies%20and%20governance%20have%20contributed%20to%20a%20robust%20and%20expanding%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20economy%20is%20often%20associated%20with%20job%20creation.%20A%20rising%20GDP%20could%20convey%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20have%20led%20to%20increased%20employment%20opportunities.%20And%20this%20could%20be%20a%20crucial%20factor%20for%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20such%20claims%20could%20help%20establish%20a%20growing%20confidence%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20stability%20among%20the%20voters%2C%20a%20crucial%20aspect%20for%20any%20citizen%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20GDP%20also%20attracts%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20investments%2C%20showing%20that%20the%20country%20is%20economically%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasically%2C%20the%20news%20of%20a%20strong%20GDP%20can%20influence%20public%20perception%20and%20confidence%20that%20the%20ruling%20government%20is%20effectively%20managing%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-hollowness-of-modi-governments-tall-claims-and-self-praise-on-economy%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollowness%20of%20the%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Tall%20Claims%20and%20Self-Praise%20on%20Economy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20real%20growth%20figures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20governor%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthelogicalindian.com%2Ftrending%2Fformer-rbi-governor-raghuram-rajan-comments-27383%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20goal%20to%20make%20India%20a%20%245%20trillion%20economy%20by%202024-25%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20aspirational%20than%20a%20carefully%20computed%20one%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20who%20will%20gain%20if%20India%20reaches%20the%20%245%20trillion%20economy%20mark%20in%202024%3F%20Will%20a%20%245%20trillion%20economy%20or%20a%20good%20income%20and%20job%20matter%20to%20ordinary%20Indians%2C%20belonging%20to%20the%20lower%2C%20lower-middle%2C%20and%20middle%20class%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20crucial%20to%20address%20the%20employment%20needs%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20youth.%20According%20to%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fraghuram-rajan-says-indias-current-growth-isnt-enough-to-create-ample-jobs%2Farticleshow%2F105117130.cms%5C%22%3ERajan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20needs%20to%20grow%20by%20over%208%25%20to%20meet%20the%20job%20demands%20of%20its%20vast%20population.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mospi.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpublication_reports%2FAR_PLFS_2022_23N.pdf%3Fdownload%3D1%5C%22%3EPeriodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20July%202022%20to%20June%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funpaid-labour-on-the-rise-muslims-not-looking-for-work-what-the-plfs-data-reveals%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20individuals%20in%20India%20are%20engaging%20in%20self-employment%20or%20unpaid%20labour.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20has%20reached%20a%20six-year%20low%2C%20standing%20at%203.2%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20unpaid%20labour%20boosting%20India%E2%80%99s%20employment%20figures%3F%20As%20many%20as%2057.3%25%20of%20the%20workers%20are%20now%20self-employed.%20This%20share%20was%2052.2%25%20six%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20economies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unequal%20countries%2C%20with%20rising%20poverty%20and%20an%20%E2%80%98affluent%20elite%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremium%20car%20sales%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fspecials%2Fspeeding-on-unbalanced-wheels-car-sales-data-reveals-increasing-inequality-in-india-1211941.html%5C%22%3Esurge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20entry-level%20vehicles%20find%20fewer%20buyers%3B%20cookie%20demand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fcons-products%2Ffmcg%2Fcookie-demand-grows-while-biscuit-sales-slow%2Farticleshow%2F70851123.cms%5C%22%3Egrows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20biscuit%20sales%20slow%3B%20and%20India%20is%20turning%20into%20a%20magnet%20for%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fservices%2Fretail%2Findia-turning-into-magnet-for-foreign-luxury-brands%2Farticleshow%2F103225218.cms%5C%22%3E%20luxury%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20FMCG%20(f%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3East%20moving%20consumer%20goods%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E)%20sales%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%5C%22%3Eare%20undergoing%20a%20slowdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20these%20are%20telltale%20signs%20of%20a%20K-shaped%2C%20or%20an%20uneven%2C%20economic%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20economic%20issues%20such%20as%20high%20inflation%20and%20crony%20capitalism%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20majoritarian%20politics%20and%20press%20freedom%20also%20impact%20the%20overall%20growth%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Deloitte%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FIndustry%2Fmental-health-issues-cost-indian-firms-14-bn-a-year-says-deloitte%2Farticle65866768.ece%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Indian%20companies%20could%20suffer%20a%20loss%20of%20%2414%20billion%20a%20year%20due%20to%20poor%20mental%20health%20among%20employees.%20A%20psychiatrist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fwe-need-more-mental-health-care-professionals-in-india%2Farticleshow%2F66146320.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20many%20Indian%20psychiatrists%20are%20moving%20abroad%20for%20%E2%80%9Cgreener%20pastures%E2%80%9D.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20leading%20to%20a%20shortage%20of%20psychiatrists%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6341936%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%3C%2Fa%3E%200.75%20psychiatrists%20per%20100%2C000%20population.%20The%20desirable%20number%20is%20anything%20above%20three%20psychiatrists%20per%20100%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Jayati%20Ghosh%2C%20in%20a%20paper%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.openedition.org%2Fsamaj%2F6882%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindutva%2C%20Economic%20Neoliberalism%20and%20the%20Abuse%20of%20Economic%20Statistics%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20explained%20how%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20at%20implementing%20the%20Hindutva%20agenda%20adversely%20affect%20economic%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had