%20social%20life.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fifth%20added%2C%20''There%20is%20no%20dichotomy%2C%20people%20just%20want%20a%20better%20life.%20On%20average%20a%20middle-income%20person%20has%20a%20far%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20outside.%20None%20of%20those%20NRIs%20would%20wanna%20come%20back%20to%20India%2C%20they%20just%20want%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20so-called%20Alpha.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India%20had%20the%20largest%20diaspora%20population%20in%20the%20world%20with%2018%20million%20people%20from%20the%20country%20living%20outside%20their%20homeland%20in%202020%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700642280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-08%2Fn3f0si38_nithin-kamath-zerodha-twitter_625x300_29_August_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbitten-by-the-bug-zerodhas-nithin-kamath-questions-why-indians-are-still-moving-to-us-4595879%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20what%20he%20termed%20a%20''dichotomy''%2C%20he%20stated%20while%20many%20rich%20Americans%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20India%2C%20young%20Indians%20prefer%20to%20move%20to%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbitten-by-the-bug-zerodhas-nithin-kamath-questions-why-indians-are-still-moving-to-us-4595879%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbitten-by-the-bug-zerodhas-nithin-kamath-questions-why-indians-are-still-moving-to-us-4595879%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbitten-by-the-bug-zerodhas-nithin-kamath-questions-why-indians-are-still-moving-to-us-4595879%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gautam%20Singhania's%20Separation%20From%20Wife%20Erases%20Rs%201%2C500%20Crore%20At%20Raymond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERaymond%20Ltd.%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20p