costing%20a%20man%20his%20own%20life%20after%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20speeding%20truck%20just%20as%20he%20was%20about%20to%20leave%20the%20site%20of%20the%20crash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20near%20Kargil%20Chowk%20in%20Southwest%20Delhi%20on%20November%203%20and%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20Monday.%20In%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%2C%20Amarjeet%20Singh%20said%20he%20was%20headed%20to%20Gurugram%20around%2010.20%20pm%20on%20November%203%20when%20his%20car%20was%20hit%20from%20behind%20by%20a%20motorcycle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmarjeet%20was%20travelling%20with%20an%20employee%20of%20his%20tea%20shop%20and%2C%20when%20they%20got%20down%20to%20investigate%2C%20they%20saw%20that%20the%20biker%20appeared%20to%20be%20drunk%20and%20had%20suffered%20a%20head%20injury%2C%20the%20FIR%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20stopped%20to%20help%20and%20another%20motorcyclist%2C%2046-year-old%20Shamsher%20Singh%2C%20was%20among%20them.%20The%20police%20were%20called%20and%20while%20everyone%20was%20waiting%20for%20them%20to%20arrive%2C%20another%20man%20offered%20to%20take%20the%20injured%20biker%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20his%20car.%20Amarjeet%20and%20Shamsher%20helped%20the%20injured%20man%20into%20the%20car%20and%20it%20left%20for%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20states%20that%20just%20as%20Shamsher%20headed%20towards%20his%20bike%20to%20go%20home%2C%20he%20was%20hit%20hard%20by%20a%20speeding%20water%20tanker.%20The%20force%20of%20the%20impact%20was%20so%20high%20that%20he%20was%20flung%20into%20the%20air%20before%20landing%20on%20the%20road.%20When%20the%20tea%20shop%20employee%20told%20Amarjeet%20what%20had%20happened%2C%20he%20got%20into%20his%20car%20and%20began%20chasing%20the%20water%20tanker.%20He%20managed%20to%20overtake%20the%20tanker%20around%20the%20Goyla%20Dairy%20area%20but%20the%20driver%20stopped%20the%20vehicle%20and%20ran%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShamsher%2