rs-early-picks-for-t20-world-cup-2024-squad-4594193%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20Reasons%20Why%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Have%20Gone%20Off-Track%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20railways%20has%20been%20facing%20criticism%20for%20prioritising%20AC%20coaches%20over%20their%20sleeper%20counterparts%2C%20with%20concerns%20raised%20about%20poor%20maintenance%20and%20heightened%20scrutiny%20regarding%20accidents%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20recent%20one%20in%20Balasore%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20horrific%20in%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20reasons%20why%20the%20Indian%20railways%20has%20been%20performing%20poorly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Poor%20operating%20ratio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%2C%20the%20finances%20of%20the%20Indian%20railways%20slipped%20into%20%E2%80%9Cconcern%20zone%E2%80%9D%20in%202021-%E2%80%9922%20as%20it%20recorded%20its%20worst%20ever%20operating%20ratio%20of%20107.39%25.%20This%20means%20that%20during%20that%20year%2C%20the%20Railways%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%20107%20to%20earn%20Rs%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20initially%20tried%20to%20blame%20the%20pandemic%20for%20the%20railways%E2%80%99%20poor%20financial%20condition%2C%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1059269%2Fwhy-the-indian-railways-is-on-the-brink%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20the%20operating%20ratio%20worsened%20sharply%20around%20four%20years%20before%20the%20pandemic%20in%202016%20and%20has%20stayed%20close%20to%20100%25%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20railways%20books%20shows%20that%20the%20failure%20to%20generate%20enough%20revenue%20surplus%20is%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20poor%20shape%20of%20its%20financials%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20notes.%20It%20highlights%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20numbers%2C%20how%20critical%20this%20failure%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20and%20how%20wide%20the%20deficit%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Misuse%20of%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20CAG%20report%20from%20December%202022%20showed%20that%20funds%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Rail%20Sanraksha%20Kosh%20(RRSK)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20special%20fund%20created%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202017%20to%20improve%20railway%20safety%20%E2%80%93%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-shows-indian-railways-misused-safety-fund-to-buy-foot-massagers-crockery-jackets%5C%22%3Espent%20on%20foot%20massagers%2C%20crockery%2C%20electrical%20appliances%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20furniture%2C%20winter%20jackets%2C%20computers%20and%20escalators%2C%20developing%20gardens%2C%20building%20toilets%2C%20paying%20salaries%20and%20bonuses%20and%20erecting%20a%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20should%20have%20received%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20each%20year%20%E2%80%93%20with%20Rs%2015%2C000%20from%20the%20Union%20and%20Rs%205%2C000%20from%20the%20railways%E2%80%99s%20revenues.%20However%2C%20over%20a%20four-year%20period%2C%20the%20Indian%20railways%20was%20only%20able%20to%20drum%20up%20Rs%204%2C225%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20a%20shortfall%20of%20Rs%2015%2C775%20crore%20in%20their%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Poor%20maintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20auditor%20has%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020-%E2%80%9921%2C%20the%20railways%20needed%20to%20replace%20old%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2094%2C873%20crore%20from%20the%20Depreciation%20Reserve%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20this%2C%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20the%20funds%20or%20Rs%2058%2C459%20crore%20were%20to%20be%20used%20for%20renewal%20of%20tracks.%20However%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20says%20only%20Rs%20671.92%20crore%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-shows-indian-railways-misused-safety-fund-to-buy-foot-massagers-crockery-jackets%5C%22%3E0.7%25%20of%20the%20funds%20were%20used%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20when%20a%202015%20white%20paper%20by%20the%20government%20said%20that%204%2C500%20km%20of%20track%20should%20be%20renewed%20annually.%20Since%20then%2C%20this%20has%20not%20happened%20in%20a%20single%20year%20till%20at%20least%202021-%E2%80%9922.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Overcrowding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20been%20systematically%20replacing%20Sleeper%20and%20Second%20Class%20coaches%20with%20AC%20coaches%20in%20various%20train%20services.%20A%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20that%20in%20four%20pairs%20of%20trains%20operating%20out%20of%20Mangaluru%20Central%20Railway%20Station%2C%20one%20Sleeper%20Coach%20each%20was%20replaced%20by%20an%20AC%203%20tier%20Economy%20Class%20coach%20each%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20Subsequently%2C%20an%20AC%203%20tier%20Economy%20Class%20coach%20was%20introduced%20in%20place%20of%20a%20general%20Second%20Class%20coach%20each%20in%20Bagmati%20Superfast%20Express%2C%20Rapti%20Sagar%20Superfast%20Express%20and%20Muzaffarpur%20Express%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20holding%20an%20unreserved%20ticket%20to%20travel%20in%20General%20Coaches%20also%20may%20find%20it%20tough%20to%20get%20seats.%20With%20a%20relatively%20smaller%20share%20of%20people%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20higher%20costs%20of%20AC%20coaches%2C%20and%20in%20scenarios%20where%20alternative%20arrangements%20are%20not%20possible%2C%20incidents%20of%20general%20ticket%20holders%20making%20their%20way%20into%20reserved%20compartments%20have%20become%20common%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20zone%20wise%20comparison%20indicated%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20AC%20seats%20in%20the%20Central%2C%20Northern%20and%20Western%20Railways%2C%20while%20the%20rise%20in%20Southern%20and%20Eastern%20Railways%20was%20not%20that%20steep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20railways%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20other%20than%20reduction%20in%20non-AC%20coaches%2C%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20the%20fully%20unreserved%20Jan%20Sadharan%20trains%20after%20the%20pandemic%20was%20also%20contributing%20to%20overcrowding.%20These%20trains%20were%20discontinued%20because%20of%20their%20unprofitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Lack%20of%20punctuality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20noted%20that%20the%20number%20of%20mail%20and%20express%20trains%20that%20were%20punctual%20declined%20from%2079%25%20in%202012-%E2%80%9913%20to%2069.23%25%20in%202018-%E2%80%9919.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-shows-indian-railways-misused-safety-fund-to-buy-foot-massagers-crockery-jackets%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20average%20speed%20of%20passenger%20trains%20in%20India%20had%20declined%20by%20more%20than%205%20km%20per%20hour%20as%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%20For%20freight%20trains%2C%20the%20average%20speed%20fell%20by%20almost%206%20km%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700639068000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffive-reasons-according-to-reports-why-the-indian-railways-have-gone-off-track%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20on%20the%20Railways%20published%20on%20various%20outlets%20point%20to%20a%20misuse%20of%20funds%20and%20its%20consistent%20inability%20to%20generate%20profits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%