iness-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fbanks-nbfcs-need-to-be-watchful-of-stress-building-up-shaktikanta-das-123112200410_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fbanks-nbfcs-need-to-be-watchful-of-stress-building-up-shaktikanta-das-123112200410_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fbanks-nbfcs-need-to-be-watchful-of-stress-building-up-shaktikanta-das-123112200410_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Myanmar%20Junta's%20Airstrikes%20Have%20Taken%20320%20Civilian%20Lives%20in%209%20Months%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22130146%2F53104499348_62c9b83fdd_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20As%20many%20as%20320%20civilians%20and%20108%20volunteers%20of%20the%20public%20defence%20force%20resisting%20the%20Myanmar%20coup%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20air%20strikes%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20junta%20between%20October%202022%20and%20June%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbacs.mm%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20report%20of%20a%20study%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%2C%20put%20together%20by%20Burma%20Affairs%20and%20Conflict%20Study%20based%20on%20publicly%20accessible%20information%20including%20news%20reports%2C%20said%20that%20in%20the%20nine%20month%20period%2C%20as%20many%20as%20395%20air%20strikes%20were%20conducted%20by%20the%20Military%20Council.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20airstrikes%20can%20be%20categorised%20into%20three%20types%3A%20exclusive%20jet%20fighter%20strikes%2C%20exclusive%20helicopter%C2%A0%20attacks%2C%C2%A0%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20both.%20Among%20these%2C%20exclusive%20jet%20fighter%20strikes%20were%20the%20most%20prevalent.%C2%A0%20During%20the%209-months%20of%20monitoring%2C%C2%A0%20a%20minimum%20of%20108%20revolutionary%20volunteers%20and%C2%A0%20at%20least%20320%20civilians%20lost%20their%20lives%20due%20to%20these%20airstrikes%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report%20put%20out%20by%20the%20non-governmental%20watch%20group%20on%20its%20Facebook%20page%20this%20November%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20such%20air%20strikes%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20the%20second%20highest%20in%20Karen%20state%20and%20the%20third%20highest%20in%20the%20Chin%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20helicopter%20attacks%20were%20mainly%20used%20in%20Sagaing%2C%20Magway%2C%20Karen%20State%2C%20Shah%20State%20and%20Rakhine%20State%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20these%20regions%20are%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Indian%20border.%20This%20January%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fone-of-5-bombs-launched-by-myanmar-army-against-rebels-landed-in-mizoram-say-locals%5C%22%3E%C2%A0residents%20of%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Champai%20district%20claimed%20that%20five%20aerial%20bombs%20dropped%20on%20a%20rebel%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Chin%20State%20by%20the%20Myanmarese%20army%20had%20landed%20on%20the%20Indian%20side.%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20who%20were%20guarding%20that%20border%2C%20later%20denied%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20attacks%20on%20the%20border%20villages%20are%2C%20however%2C%20considered%20as%20the%20cause%20behind%20a%20refugee%20influx%20into%20Mizoram.%20Early%20this%20week%2C%20about%205%2C000%20such%20refugees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmyanmar-refugees-take-shelter-in-mizoram-champhai-after-fleeing-from-their-country-following-airstrike-1643087%5C%22%3Eentered%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Champai%20district%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20air%20strikes%20on%20the%20Chin%20State.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Military%20Council%2C%20in%20order%20to%20justify%20their%20airstrikes%2C%20claims%20that%20they%20attack%20only%20military%20targets%20and%20deny%20civilian%20targets%2C%20but%20data%20shows%20that%20one%20third%20of%20all%20air%20strikes%C2%A0%20do%20hit%20civilian%20targets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20airstrikes%2C%20strikes%20during%20combat%20was%20the%20most%20with%20247%20times%2C%20followed%20by%2064%20attacks%20on%20villages%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20combat.%20The%20airstrikes%20on%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20revolutionary%20forces%20were%20the%20third%20highest%20with%2043%20times%2C%20which%20is%20a%20point%20to%20be%20aware%20of.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20was%20also%20seen%20that%20air%20strikes%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20civilian%20targets%20such%20as%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20(IDPs)%20camps%2C%20churches%2C%20clinics%2C%20workplaces%2C%20schools%2C%20monasteries%20and%20celebratory%20gatherings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20names%20eight%20military%20airfields%20from%20where%20these%20strikes%20have%20been%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20pro-democracy%20rebel%20militias%20have%20succeeded%20in%20inflicting%20massive%20setbacks%20to%20the%20junta%20on%20the%20ground%20lately%2C%20these%20air%20strikes%20by%20the%20military%20have%20come%20to%20them%20as%20significant%20hurdles.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700638396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22130146%2F53104499348_62c9b83fdd_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-junta-airstrikes-mizoram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20pro-democracy%20rebel%20militias%