ext%3DIn%2520his%2520statement%252C%2520the%2520Attorney%2CScheme%2520will%2520not%2520be%2520illegal.%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know%20who%20has%20contributed%20how%20much%20to%20which%20political%20party.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20statement%20was%20intended%20to%20counter%20the%20very%20legitimate%20demand%20for%20a%20more%20extensive%20VVPAT%20verification%20of%20the%20votes%20cast%20in%20the%20EVMs%2C%20the%20second%20was%20in%20response%20to%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20which%20have%20effectively%20become%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20private%20ATM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20never%20been%20in%20doubt%20that%20these%20statements%20are%20a%20faithful%20expression%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20private%20views%2C%20but%20the%20sheer%20brazenness%20of%20declaring%20it%20openly%20%E2%80%95%20and%20in%20court!%20%E2%80%95%20is%20mind-blowing.%20It%20is%20beyond%20arrogance%20and%20hubris%2C%20it%20shows%20utter%20contempt%20for%20the%20public%2C%20the%20constitution%20and%20(dare%20I%20say%20it%3F)%20even%20for%20the%20highest%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETranslated%20into%20language%20which%20we%20porkers%20can%20understand%2C%20the%20government%20is%20actually%20saying%3A%20we%20will%20have%20our%20way%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20a%20tinker%E2%80%99s%20cuss%20for%20what%20the%20citizenry%20thinks%20or%20what%20the%20court%20decides%3B%20we%20have%20the%20majority%20in%20Parliament%20(even%20if%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20her%20Louis%20Vuitton%20bags%20are%20not%20expelled)%20and%20can%20pass%20any%20ordinance%20or%20Bill%20we%20are%20inclined%20to.%20Misplaced%20confidence%20and%20hubris%2C%20did%20you%20say%3F%20You%20would%20be%20wrong%2C%20dear%20reader%2C%20because%20past%20events%20have%20proved%20that%20they%20are%20right.%20The%20judiciary%20has%20never%20been%20an%20obstacle%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20rampaging%20depredation%20of%20our%20social%2C%20constitutional%2C%20legal%20and%20institutional%20landscape.%20One%20cannot%20help%20feeling%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20impudence%20is%20due%20in%20no%20small%20measure%20to%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20accommodating%20and%20obliging%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20never%20fails%20to%20disappoint%2C%20like%20on%20the%20petition%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Fsupreme-court-same-sex-marriage-lgbtqi%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520apex%2520court%2520said%2520that%2Ccouples%2520and%2520take%2520corrective%2520measures.%5C%22%3Elegalising%20same%20sex%20marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-supreme-court-bail-justice-khanna%5C%22%3EManish%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20were%20vehemently%20opposed%20by%20the%20government.%20Both%20were%20dismissed%2C%20quite%20against%20the%20run%20of%20play.%20Both%20judgments%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%2C%20not%20only%20because%20of%20their%20inherent%20contradictions%2C%20but%20also%20because%20in%20comments%2C%20the%20court%20had%20appeared%20to%20favour%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20in%20the%20same%20sex%20marriage%20case%20is%20retrogressive%20and%20mired%20in%20a%20medieval%20mindset%2C%20which%20exposes%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20disconnect%20with%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20social%20order.%20By%20refusing%20to%20legalise%20same%20sex%20marriages%2C%20or%20allowing%20same%20sex%20couples%20to%20adopt%20or%20giving%20them%20civil%20rights%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20the%20court%20may%20have%20warmed%20the%20cockles%20of%20the%20BJP%2FRSS%20heart%20but%20it%20has%20also%20given%20a%20thumbs%20up%20to%20obscurantist%20forces.%20By%20directing%20the%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20under%20the%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20to%20examine%20conferring%20more%20rights%20on%20queer%20people%2C%20the%20court%20is%20displaying%20its%20naivete%2C%20or%20deliberately%20deluding%20itself%3A%20does%20it%20really%20expect%20an%20officer%20who%20is%20on%20extension%20in%20service%20and%20who%20has%20been%20party%20to%20every%20unilateral%20and%20illiberal%C2%A0%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20present%20regime%2C%20to%20propose%20any%20expansion%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20this%20section%2C%20which%20this%20government%20is%20vociferously%20opposed%20to%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20logic%20in%20the%20Manish%20Sisodia%20case%20is%20even%20more%20difficult%20to%20comprehend.%20The%20court%20had%20time%20and%20again%20castigated%20the%20prosecution%20for%20lack%20of%20evidence.%20It%20had%20even%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20money%20trail%20to%20link%20Sisodia%20with%20any%20bribe%2C%20and%20that%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20case%20would%20collapse%20during%20trial.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20denied%20him%20bail.%20This%20can%20only%20encourage%20the%20government%20to%20lock%20up%20more%20people%2C%20confident%20that%20the%20courts%20will%20not%20offer%20bail.%20Clearly%2C%20this%20order%20is%20based%20more%20on%20presumption%20than%20on%20solid%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-supreme-court-bail-justice-khanna%5C%22%3EThe%20Real%20Mystery%20of%20the%20Manish%20Sisodia%20Case%20Is%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20About-Face%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20question%20was%20taken%20up%20after%20five%20years%2C%20the%20delay%20allowing%20the%20BJP%20to%20mop%20up%20almost%20Rs%205%2C500%20crore%2C%20more%20than%20all%20other%20parties%20combined.%20The%20court%20concluded%20hearings%20and%20reserved%20its%20order%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20again%20giving%20the%20BJP%20the%20opportunity%20to%20open%20the%20window%20for%20another%20tranche%20this%20week.%20This%20will%20enable%20it%20to%20secure%20all%20the%20donations%20it%20needs%20for%20the%202024%20elections%3A%20whatever%20the%20court%20now%20decides%20will%20be%20irrelevant%20for%20the%20coming%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Maharashtra%20case%20between%20the%20two%20Shiv%20Sena%20factions%2C%20the%20Speaker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-shiv-sena-uddhav-thackeray-eknath-shinde%5C%22%3Econtinues%20to%20ignore%2C%20if%20not%20defy%2C%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20orders%20for%20a%20quick%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Speaker%20has%20been%20given%20a%20long%20rope%20that%20he%20is%20using%20to%20strangle%20whatever%20vestiges%20of%20democracy%20remain.%20The%20Article%20370%20case%20similarly%20hangs%20in%20limbo%2C%20the%20orders%20reserved%2C%20and%20democracy%20continues%20to%20elude%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%20has%20disappeared%20from%20the%20radar%2C%20if%20not%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20registry.%20Whatever%20happened%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpegasus-spyware-supreme-court-truth%5C%22%3EPegasus%20Committee%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20into%20the%20Adani%20conglomerate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20day%E2%80%99s%20delay%20in%20deciding%20such%20crucial%20cases%2C%20or%20in%20delivering%20reserved%20orders%2C%20the%20status%20quo%20(which%20can%20only%20favour%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day)%20becomes%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Efait%20accompli%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20all%20the%20more%20difficult%20to%20reverse.%20It%20emboldens%20the%20government%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20bulldozer%20tactics%2C%20and%20to%20take%20the%20court%20for%20granted.%20Which%20is%20why%20the%20Attorney%20General%20can%20make%20the%20kind%20of%20statements%20he%20does%20and%20continue%20cocking%20a%20snook%20at%20the%20court.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20he%20even%20cautioned%20the%20court%20not%20to%20cross%20its%20limits%2C%20when%20the%20CJI%20fixed%20December%2031%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20Speaker%20to%20decide%20the%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20disqualification%20case!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20that%20the%20court%20wishes%20to%20avoid%20a%20confrontation%20with%20the%20executive%2C%20and%20therefore%20%E2%80%9Curges%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20should%20direct%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Crequests%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20should%20mandate%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Cpersuades%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20should%20command.%20But%20such%20a%20timid%20approach%20is%20not%20working%3B%20it%20takes%20two%20to%20avoid%20a%20clash%2C%20and%20this%20government%20is%20perpetually%20in%20adversarial%20mode.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20also%20reduces%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20law%20and%20dilutes%20the%20credibility%20of%20legal%20institutions%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20citizenry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20the%20court%20to%20administer%20the%20law%20without%20fear%20or%20favour%2C%20to%20practise%20within%20the%20court%20what%20it%20preaches%20in%20keynote%20speeches.%20We%20need%20less%20rhetoric%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eobiter%20dicta%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20moral%20grandstanding%20from%20the%20judiciary%20and%20more%20concern%20for%20foundational%20freedoms%20and%20rights%2C%20stern%20messaging%20to%20the%20government%2C%20and%20imposition%20of%20consequences%20for%20defying%20orders.%20%E2%80%98Stooping%20to%20conquer%E2%80%99%20may%20be%20an%20interesting%20phrase%20for%20an%20Oliver%20Goldsmith%20play%2C%20but%20entirely%20inappropriate%20for%20our%20current%20political%20environment%3B%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98flattering%20to%20deceive%E2%80%99%20may%20describe%20it%20better%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%2C%20first%20published%C2%A0on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20blog%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F10f04ed6-4773-40d2-9879-0dd3637ecaf3%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F10f04ed6-4773-40d2-9879-0dd3637ecaf3%3Fj%253DeyJ1Ijo