an%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJack%20Smith%2C%20a%20long-time%20federal%20prosecutor%2C%20was%20appointed%20to%20watch%20over%20investigations%20into%20allegations%20of%20transgressing%20national%20security%20and%20being%20party%20to%20electoral%20malpractices%20against%20Trump.%20In%20the%20year%20since%2C%20the%20legal%20dragnet%20around%20him%20has%20become%20larger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20charges%20against%20Trump%2C%20it%20is%20now%20imperative%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20explain%20the%20unprecedented%20political%20support%20he%20lent%20to%20Trump%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20September%202019.%20With%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20due%20in%20months%2C%20an%20explanation%20at%20least%2C%20if%20not%20an%20expression%20of%20regret%2C%20is%20warranted%20at%20the%20earliest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20owes%20a%20statement%20on%20record%20to%20the%20people.%20He%20must%20clarify%20why%20during%20that%20visit%20he%20gave%20the%20unjustifiable%20call%20for%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fhowdy-modi-houston-narendra-modi-donald-trump%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAbki%20bar%2C%20Trump%20sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20(This%20time%2C%20a%20Trump%20administration)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20near%20replay%20of%20his%20successful%202014%20slogan%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Howdy%20Modi%E2%80%99%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Texas%20India%20Forum%2C%20at%20Houston.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20the%20two%20cases%20under%20Smith%E2%80%99s%20watch%2C%20Trump%20further%20stands%20indicted%20in%20an%20anti-corruption%20case%20involving%20moral%20turpitude%2C%20in%20New%20York.%20He%20faces%20trial%20on%20charges%20of%20paying%20sex%20hush%20money%20to%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20the%20pornographic%20film%20actress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20Trump%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20committing%20extremely%20grave%20electoral%20malpractices%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Georgia.%20This%20accusation%20mirrors%20one%20of%20the%20two%20federal%20cases.%20He%20also%20action%20in%20the%20case%20filed%20by%20journalist%20and%20author%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20where%20far-reaching%20allegations%20against%20Trump%20relate%20to%20rape%20and%20defamation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParadoxically%2C%20these%20developments%20will%20not%20impede%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20intended%20candidature%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20polls%20and%20are%20unlikely%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20assuming%20office%20in%20January%202025%2C%20if%20elected.%20The%20peculiarity%20of%20American%20jurisprudence%20is%20such%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20such%20a%20development%2C%20Trump%20may%20well%20become%20the%20first%20American%20First%20Citizen%20to%20pardon%20himself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20does%20not%20permit%20Modi%20to%20remain%20silent%20over%20his%20grave%20indiscretion%20and%20an%20error%20of%20judgement%20in%202019.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20visit%2C%20Modi%20was%20riding%20a%20crest%20after%20being%20re-elected%20with%20an%20enhanced%20majority%20and%20he%20possibly%20assumed%20that%20Trump%20too%20would%20be%20re-elected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20reading%20was%20further%20reinforced%20when%20the%20US%20president%20visited%20India%20in%20February%202020%20and%20the%20red%20carpet%20was%20rolled%20for%20him%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20It%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20during%20his%20two-day%20visit%20beginning%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20political%20bastion%2C%20Trump%20addressed%20a%20%E2%80%98Namaste%20Trump%E2%80%99%20rally%20before%20an%20unprecedented%20one%20lakh%20plus%20audience%20at%20the%20Motera%20stadium%20(before%20it%20was%20renamed).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rally%20followed%20a%20massive%2022%20km%20road%20show%20from%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20airport%20to%20the%20stadium%20with%20Trump%2C%20his%20wife%20Melania%20and%20Modi%20at%20its%20head.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20were%20lined%20up%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20sanitised%20streets.%20Giant%20billboards%20were%20put%20up%20for%20the%20event%2C%20called%20India%20Road%20Show%20by%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20municipal%20corporation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20event%2C%20while%20Delhi%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Ffeb%2F25%2Fdelhi-rocked-by-deadly-protests-during-donald-trumps-india-visit%5C%22%3Emost%20horrifying%20communal%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20recent%20history%2C%20was%20dubbed%20a%20rare%20instance%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20dynamic%20personalities%E2%80%9D%20coming%20together%20for%20%E2%80%9Cone%20momentous%20occasion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20explanation%20from%20Modi%20for%20his%20inappropriate%20support%20to%20Trump%20when%20he%20had%20already%20begun%20campaigning%20for%20the%202020%20polls%20which%20he%20eventually%20lost%2C%20is%20all%20the%20more%20inescapable%20because%20Modi%20has%20declared%20that%20in%20his%20re-election%20bid%20in%202024%2C%20corruption%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20pillars%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20plank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20plethora%20of%20raids%20and%20cases%20against%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20opposition%20parties%20and%20leaders%20are%20cited%20to%20buttress%20his%20claim%20and%20Modi%20is%20claiming%20to%20be%20a%20ceaseless%20crusader%20against%20graft.%20It%20would%20thereby%20be%20extremely%20duplicitous%20if%20Modi%20does%20not%20explain%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eerror%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202019%20in%20backing%20Trump.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20accusation%20against%20Trump%20in%20the%20New%20York%20case%20is%20that%20he%20bought%20Stormy%20Daniels%E2%80%99%20silence.%20Because%20of%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20charge%20and%20prima%20facie%20evidence%2C%20Trump%20has%20become%20the%20first%20former%20US%20President%20to%20be%20indicted.%20He%20faces%20as%20many%20as%2034%20felony%20charges%20and%20can%20be%20sentenced%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20a%20staggering%20136%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14155328%2F1620px-Donald_Trump_39630669575.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14155328%2F1620px-Donald_Trump_39630669575.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14155328%2F1620px-Donald_Trump_39630669575-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14155328%2F1620px-Donald_Trump_39630669575-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F14155328%2F1620px-Donald_Trump_39630669575-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-658081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump.%20Photo%3A%20Gage%20Skidmore%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20enormity%20of%20alleged%20crimes%20for%20which%20Trump%20faces%20multiple%20trials%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20for%20Modi%20to%20confess%20his%20lack%20of%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20the%20former%20president%E2%80%99s%20misdemeanours.%20Peculiarly%2C%20the%20silence%20of%20opposition%20parties%20on%20this%20matter%20so%20far%20is%20not%20just%20stupefying%2C%20but%20also%20indicative%20of%20their%20short%20memories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%202019%20tour%20to%20the%20US%20opened%20with%20the%20community%20summit%2C%20Howdy%20Modi%2C%20at%20Houston%2C%20Texas%20with%20Trump%20by%20his%20side.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-49788492%5C%22%3EBBC%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal-touch%20diplomacy%20with%20Mr%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20bear%20hugs%20was%20played%20to%20perfection.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20slogan%2C%20modelled%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20winning%202014%20slogan%2C%20was%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20picked%20up%20from%20a%20Trump%20video%20aimed%20at%20American%20voters%20of%20Indian%20origin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20was%20not%20alone%20in%20his%20choice%20of%20hyperbolic%20praise.%20Trump%20too%2C%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20declared%20that%20the%20Indian%20premier%20was%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20greatest%2C%20most%20devoted%20and%20most%20loyal%20friends.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20endorsed%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20performance%20by%20declaring%20that%20Modi%20was%20consistently%20doing%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctruly%20exceptional%20job%20for%20India%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20criticised%20Modi%20at%20that%20time%20for%20backing%20Trump.%20This%20forced%20foreign%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fjaishankar-clarifies-pm-modi-abki-baar-trump-sarkar-call-1604991-2019-10-01%5C%22%3Eassert%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20not%20endorsed%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20candidature%2C%20but%20merely%20reiterated%20words%20the%20American%20president%20used%20in%20a%20campaign%20video%20aimed%20at%20the%20American%20Indian%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0But%2C%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20it%20appeared%20that%20Modi%20was%20calling%20for%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20in%20the%20impending%202020%20polls%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitically%2C%20the%20most%20serious%20charge%20against%20Trump%20is%20related%20to%20electoral%20malpractice.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20former%20US%20president%20was%20indicted%20for%20attempting%20to%20overturn%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20presidential%20election.%20The%20specific%20charges%20are%20attempts%20to%20defraud%20the%20nation%2C%20tampering%20with%20witnesses%2C%20targeting%20citizen%20rights%2C%20and%20obstructing%20official%20proceedings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrump%20stands%20accused%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20storming%20and%20laying%20siege%20to%20the%20US%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%20to%20prevent%20the%20vice%20president%20at%20that%20time%2C%20Mike%20Pence%2C%20from%20certifying%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20winner%2C%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%20incumbent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrump%20is%20further%20accused%20of%20pushing%20efforts%20to%20prepare%20fake%20elector%20slates%20and%20reverse%20the%20results%20from%20several%20states.%20This%20played%20a%20central%20role%20in%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cseven-part%20plan%E2%80%9D%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20that%20in%20India%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20impartiality%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20questioned%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20disregard%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20at%20subverting%20the%20electoral%20system%20and%20not%20accept%20his%20personal%20miscalculation%20and%20injudiciousness%20will%20effectively%20mean%20that%20he%20condones%20the%20former%20President%E2%80%99s%20attempts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20further%20raise%20questions%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20latest%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Demolition%20and%20the%20Verdict%3A%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Project%20to%20Reconfigure%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20His%20other%20books%20include%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%3A%20Icons%20of%20the%20Indian%20Right%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%2C%20The%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40NilanjanUdwin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700636417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22121907%2Fmodi-trump-houston.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-explain-unjustifiable-abki-baar-trump-sarkar-call%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20corruption%20is%20a%20principal%20pillar%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20plank%20for%202024%2C%20Modi%20needs%20to%20explain%20his%20hyperbolic%20praise%20for%20the%20former%20US%20president%2C%20who%20is%20mired%20in%20a%20series%20of%20criminal%20probes.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-explain-unjustifiable-abki-baar-trump-sarkar-call%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20say%202%20dead%20and%205%20wounded%20in%20Philadelphia%20shooting%20that%20may%20be%20drug-related%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700635369000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105407917%2Cimgsize-30420.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpolice-say-2-dead-and-5-wounded-in-philadelphia-shooting-that-may-be-drug-related%2Farticleshow%2F105407412.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http