F2023%2F11%2F22095533%2Fimage1024x768.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Israeli%20cabinet%20approved%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20today%20a%20deal%20with%20Hamas%20which%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20release%20of%20Israeli%20hostages.%20According%20to%20Israel%2C%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20taken%20by%20the%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20during%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20will%20be%20freed%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%2C%20Hamas%20said%20Israel%20will%20release%20150%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20children%20held%20in%20Israeli%20jails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20also%20includes%20a%20four-day%20%E2%80%9Ccease-fire%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20term%20used%20by%20Hamas%2C%20while%20Israel%20has%20spoken%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpause%20in%20fighting%E2%80%9D.%20Israel%20said%20it%20would%20extend%20the%20lull%20by%20an%20additional%20day%20for%20every%2010%20hostages%20released%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20international%20relations%20office%20in%20Doha%2C%20Musa%20Abu%20Marzouq%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fsenior-hamas-leader-admits-hostage-mistake-reveals-hostage-deal-details%5C%22%3E%20had%20given%20extensive%20details%20of%20the%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%20to%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAGL3mkKQ8ng%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Top%20Hamas%20Leader%20Admits%20Taking%20Babies%20%26amp%3B%20Elderly%20Hostage%20%E2%80%9Ca%20Mistake%E2%80%9D%3B%20Reveals%20Hostage%20Deal%20Details%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20in%C2%A0%20a%20statement%2C%20welcomed%20the%20deal%20for%20a%20pause%20in%20fighting.%20He%20thanked%20the%20heads%20of%20government%20in%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar%20%E2%80%93%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al-Thani%20of%20Qatar%20and%20President%20Abdel-Fattah%20El-Sisi%20of%20Egypt%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20their%20and%20partnership%20in%20reaching%20this%20deal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar%20too%20has%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20a%20humanitarian%20pause%2C%20noting%20%E2%80%9CThe%20humanitarian%20pause%20will%20also%20allow%20the%20entry%20of%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20humanitarian%20convoys%20and%20relief%20aid%2C%20including%20fuel%20designated%20for%20humanitarian%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20State%20of%20Qatar%20announces%20that%20a%20humanitarian%20pause%20has%20been%20agreed%20in%20Gaza%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMOFAQatar%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MOFAQatar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5qqjSjvt4X%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5qqjSjvt4X%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20%E2%80%93%20Qatar%20(%40MofaQatar_EN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMofaQatar_EN%2Fstatus%2F1727170260154151248%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHamas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20Hamas%20has%20released%20an%20official%20statement%20that%20recognises%20the%20following%20terms%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20A%20ceasefire%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20a%20cessation%20of%20all%20military%20actions%20by%20occupation%20forces%20in%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20and%20a%20cessation%20of%20the%20movement%20of%20its%20military%20vehicles%20penetrating%20into%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20entry%20of%20hundreds%20of%20trucks%20of%20humanitarian%2C%20relief%2C%20medical%20and%20fuel%20aid%20into%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20without%20exception%2C%20in%20the%20north%20and%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20release%20of%2050%20women%20and%20children%20of%20the%20occupation%E2%80%99s%20detainees%2C%20all%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20years%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20150%20women%20and%20children%20of%20our%20people%20from%20the%20occupation%E2%80%99s%20prisons%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20years%2C%20in%20order%20of%20time%20imprisoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Stopping%20all%20occupation%20air%20traffic%20in%20the%20south%20for%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Stopping%20all%20occupation%20air%20traffic%20in%20the%20North%20for%206%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20from%2010%3A00%20AM%20until%204%3A00%20PM.%20During%20the%20truce%20period%2C%20the%20occupation%20is%20committed%20not%20to%20attack%20or%20arrest%20anyone%20in%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ensuring%20freedom%20of%20movement%20of%20people%20(from%20north%20to%20south)%20along%20Salah%20El-Din%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20announce%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20truce%20agreement%2C%20we%20affirm%20that%20our%20hands%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20trigger%2C%20and%20our%20victorious%20battalions%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20lookout%20to%20defend%20our%20people%20and%20defeat%20the%20occupation%20and%20aggression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetanyahu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20deal%E2%80%99s%20approval%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20stressed%20a%20pause%20in%20fighting%20would%20not%20mean%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20on%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20continue%20the%20war%20until%20we%20achieve%20all%20of%20our%20war%20aims%3A%20To%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20return%20all%20of%20our%20hostages%20and%20our%20missing%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20n