rsons-accessing-hearing-solutions-govt-jobs-skills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChild%20Of%20Deaf%20Adults%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20a%20CODA%2C%20fighting%20for%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20rights%20was%20personal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20when%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(RPwD%20Act%2C%202016)%20was%20being%20passed%2C%20I%20was%20there%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20protesting%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Delhi%20and%20interpreting%20for%20them%20with%20the%20police%20and%20other%20officials.%20I%20must%20have%20been%207%20or%208%20and%20the%20entire%20experience%20was%20quite%20scary%20because%20I%20was%20a%20child%20after%20all%20talking%20to%20adults%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sarah%2C%20now%20training%20to%20professionally%20be%20an%20Indian%20Sign%20Language%20(ISL)%20interpreter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSign%20language%20was%20my%20first%20language.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292576%2Fdeaf-mute-kashmiri-artist-carves-wooden-sculptures-earns-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoth%20my%20parents%20are%20Deaf%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20sign%20language%20is%20my%20mother%20tongue.%20That%20is%20how%20we%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-300x126.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-500x209.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-768x321.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-150x63.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0For%20more%20information%2C%20please%20feel%20free%20to%20go%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignhealth.org.uk%2Fresources%2Flearn-about-deafness%2Fdeaf-or-deaf%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWe%2520use%2520Deaf%2520with%2520a%2Clanguage%2520as%2520their%2520first%2520language.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%3C%2Fa%3E%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20CODA%20recently%20gained%20popularity%20as%20a%20film%20of%20the%20same%20name%20made%20a%20big%20splash%20at%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20in%202022.%20In%20India%2C%20the%201996%20film%20%E2%80%98Khamoshi%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Musical%E2%80%99%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20portray%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20Deaf%20community%20as%20authentically%20as%20possible.%20From%20bringing%20forth%20the%20seclusion%20experienced%20by%20CODAs%20to%20highlighting%20the%20numerous%20barriers%20for%20Deaf%20communities%2C%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20debut%20was%20well%20ahead%20of%20its%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20become%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20voice%2C%20CODAs%20grow%20up%20a%20little%20too%20quickly%2C%20often%20shedding%20innocence%20and%20befriending%20maturity%20at%20a%20tender%20age.%20These%20children%20form%20the%20bridge%20between%20the%20Deaf%20and%20hearing%20worlds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20aims%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20these%20young%20people%20doing%20incredible%20work%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%20and%20bring%20forward%20their%20lives%2C%20issues%2C%20and%20stories%20in%20everyday%20